summary: I’m looking at the Shazam! cast and Shazam is a black guy! That is like one of the 2 good things Geoff Johns did with the New 52...
body:
I’m looking at the Shazam! cast and Shazam is a black guy!

That is like one of the 2 good things Geoff Johns did with the New 52 Captain Marvel! And they kept it!

(For the record the other good thing in that comic is the introduction of Darla, Pedro and Eugene, which apparently are also in this movie)
